changeView

public void changeView(int month,
                       int year)
Gets a range of data from the DataHandler for a specified month and year, and gives it to the ViewPanel. This range includes the month and year specified, but also enough days before the 1st of the month and after the last to make the first and last weeks have seven days
Parameters:
month - the month
year - the year
